{"tid":113293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華女友狂送禮氹英男友　反遭監生虐打死","createTime":"2017-02-09T00:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T05:58:13.000Z","uid":81228,"like":81,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"433fdc3d0d22d7a4a65c28373ea073a335b20bde","tid":113293,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:00:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170207/photo/bknint-20170207180508150-0207_17011_001_01b.jpg?20170207193236\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170207%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170207180508150-0207_17011_001_01b.jpg%3F20170207193236&h=f54969b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n畢熙熙（左）與馬修斯（右）為情侶。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n<br />\n中國籍24歲留學生畢熙熙（Xixi Bi，音譯）去年8月，被發現倒卧於英國威爾斯的寓所內，疑遭23歲同居男友馬修斯（Jordan Matthews）監生打死。案件昨日繼續聆訊，預計需時3周。被告坦承看到女友手機上其他男人的訊息後發狂，但只承認誤殺而否認謀殺罪。<br />\n<br />\n庭上透露，生於中國南京、能操四種語言的畢熙熙，在卡的夫大學深造碩士時，與空手道黑帶、任職酒保的馬修斯戀上，並共賦同居。她為對方交房租、付賬和買車，男方卻常常虐打她，逼她「走堂」，更不時罵她「沒用」，但她仍對男友言聽計從。<br />\n<br />\n馬修斯曾向警方供稱，看到畢熙熙手機上另一名男人向她發訊息後，憤怒得可怕，便開始施虐。畢熙熙最終倒斃家中，馬修斯承認自己誤殺女友。惟檢控官斥馬修斯操控及長期毒打女友；並引述驗屍報告指她死於多重鈍性傷害。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，威爾斯警方於去年8月19日接報，畢熙熙在寓所呼吸困難，救援人員到場後證實她死亡。馬修斯涉嫌謀殺被捕，而死者遺體已被送返故鄉的家屬身邊。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170207/photo/bknint-20170207180508150-0207_17011_001_02b.jpg?20170207193236\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170207%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170207180508150-0207_17011_001_02b.jpg%3F20170207193236&h=ad57c09e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬修斯（右）被指常常虐打畢熙熙（左）。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170207/bknint-20170207180508150-0207_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170207%2Fbknint-20170207180508150-0207_17011_001.html&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1Wi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=f260331b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170207/bknint-20170207180508150-0207_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"44111bc7bd2bbc760d7c974960e4546a3911edc7","tid":113293,"uid":18384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:01:38.000Z","msg":"作賤自己"},{"pid":"ef36f25759a214cf1fcc23ce43335fe2b8825c1b","tid":113293,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:02:43.000Z","msg":"食洋腸呀拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ce038866da8095d20c0494005545d4cf97a9cd","tid":113293,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:03:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f7ecba929b166bcf9017b9b0655721c1c94a97f","tid":113293,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:03:25.000Z","msg":"做免費雞做到冇左條名"},{"pid":"9df573175e06ea10214a34669b9b29ba6d8593d9","tid":113293,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:05:20.000Z","msg":"留名等睇大愛撚道德撚屌連登仔落井下石冇人性<br />\n<br />\nBtw, 為左食洋腸作賤自己, 某程度上係抵死"},{"pid":"3f278f59e7223466221c53c964c62a7f012e9cc8","tid":113293,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:06:58.000Z","msg":"她為對方交房租、付賬和買車，男方卻常常虐打她，逼她「走堂」，更不時罵她「沒用」，但她仍對男友言聽計從。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b85bc88b4d76a723426701580f2769e7a2bb9c","tid":113293,"uid":50182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:10:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做免費雞做到冇左條名</blockquote><br />\n返高登啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae57a26c754d56fe5eca2868472acdaadbaac2b5","tid":113293,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:10:58.000Z","msg":"偉大既白人"},{"pid":"5a4525b66888b66bdd440ec3a6600b6d6ecb8829","tid":113293,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T00:12:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做免費雞做到冇左條名</blockquo